keyFacts: Document EFTA00002516 is a technical label for a Western Digital hard drive (model WD5003ABYX, 500GB).
The hard drive has serial number WMAYP6107485 and was manufactured on May 26, 2013.
The drive is labeled as 'Enterprise Storage' and is a product of Malaysia.
The document's inclusion in the Epstein case files suggests it relates to a seized or analyzed digital storage device as potential evidence.
